id not write. In the background, please note any articles that do not list me as the author (all my articles have a byline, \\\"By Tiny Manyonga\\\"). They don't necessarily nee to be deleted but it is worth noting. Another thing worth noting is I think I need to consider backing you up and moving you to a cloud server, incase shomething happens to my laptop. We must discuss this at the end of the day so add it to my to-do list.\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 8:56 AM (Africa/Johannesburg) / 2026-03-24 06:56 UTC\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"gateway-client\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n[Tue 2026-03-24 08:56 GMT+2] So kinda jumped the gun here. I don't mind that you wrote drafts for posts 001-006 here but my intention was for us to complete post001 for X first before restarting the progress on 002 that we had already made. Check the relevant session and you will see we were discussing 002 for LI first and our discussion was centered around NurseSphere. Did you take notes for how we created the LI post 001 for your agent creation?\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 9:04 AM (Africa/Johannesburg) / 2026-03-24 07:04 UTC\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"gateway-client\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n[Tue 2026-03-24 09:04 GMT+2] Hm, we have a real problem here because I need you to find the date when NurseSphere was first mentioned. It will be the same date as I mentioned Reclaimix. Yes, there will be multiple sessions for that date. There were problems that needed fixing. I will need you to find and read all those session files, including in the backup folders. Our setup is now working smoothly so you won't need to do this again. Please read all those files - I trust your json transcript reading s