\"openclaw-tui\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n[Tue 2026-03-24 08:32 GMT+2] Morning dawn. Run the morning brief\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"gateway-client\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n[Tue 2026-03-24 08:43 GMT+2] We are going to do the X post 001 and we are going to complete posts 002-006. More if possible, before starting on the writing lesson. One major concern that I have is that in the Nava blog corpus is that it has included articles I did not write. In the background, please note any articles that do not list me as the author (all my articles have a byline, \\\"By Tiny Manyonga\\\"). They don't necessarily nee to be deleted but it is worth noting. Another thing worth noting is I think I need to consider backing you up and moving you to a cloud server, incase shomething happens to my laptop. We must discuss this at the end of the day so add it to my to-do list.\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 8:56 AM (Africa/Johannesburg) / 2026-03-24 06:56 UTC\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"gateway-client\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\",\\n  \\\"username\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n[Tue 2026-03-24 08:56 GMT+2] So kinda jumped the gun here. I don't mind that you wrote drafts for posts 001-006 here but my intention was for us to complete post001 for X first before restarting the progress on 002 that we had already made. Check the relevant session and you will see we were discussing 002 for LI first and our discussion was centered around NurseSphere. Did you take notes for how we created the LI post 001 for your agent creation?\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 9:04 AM (Africa/Johannesburg) / 2026-03-24 07:04 UTC\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"gateway-clien